Title: Penguicon Photo Booth
Book Description: Say cheese! Grab a prop and take some pics!

Title: Chaos Machine
Book Description: This customizable marble roller coaster is a perennial favorite. It serves as a metaphor for the open source development process. The Chaos Machine is available all weekend for Penguicon attendees to tinker with!

Title: Giant Jenga
Book Description: It's your favorite party game- Jenga- but GIANT!

Title: Prize Capsule
Book Description: Put in a quarter and get a prize!

Title: Retro Gaming - Addition Errata
Book Description: Relive your childhood with our retro gaming event! From Atari to Nintendo 64 (and almost every system in between)- revel in four hours of pure time-travel joy! Located in the Lobby.
